The paper discusses algorithms in multi-agent systems from the perspective of reinforcement learning and game theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
